Disclaimer once again: I am not a doctor or professional, I am a momma sharing what worked for for my little foodie daughter. Of course there are other ways to avoid picky eaters, but this was what worked for Eva!

Please check with your pediatrician if this is safe for your baby too, and remember at the end of the day if you’ve tried your best and baby still wants to eat what they want to eat then it’s OK at least you’ve tried you’re very best. A fed baby is the best kinda baby 🥰
